target":"../卡死.md","line":362},{"title":"24春考","target":"../24春考.md","line":431},{"title":"任意存在","target":"../存在任意.md","line":440},{"title":"不定方程","target":"../不定方程.md","line":466},{"title":"函数迭代","target":"../函数迭代.md","line":471},{"title":"构造函数","target":"../构造函数.md","line":484},{"title":"y的不等式","target":"../Y的不等式.md","line":523},{"title":"图像变换","target":"../图像变换.md","line":563},{"title":"分式函数","target":"../分式函数.md","line":595},{"title":"中心对称","target":"../中心对称.md","line":600},{"title":"三角函数","target":"../三角函数.md","line":606},{"title":"图像判断","target":"../图像判断.md","line":616},{"title":"零点问题","target":"../零点.md","line":678},{"title":"0,1) \\\\ 1-|x-3|, x \\in[1,+\\infty)\\end{array}\\right.$, 则关于 $x$ 的函数 $F(x)=f(x)-a(0<a<1)$ 的所有零点之和为 $\\qquad$ （结果用 $a$ 表示）。\n                    - \n                - 练 9-2\n                    - \n                    - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}e^{(x+1)^{2}}, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ x+\\frac{4}{x}-3, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 函数 $y=f(x)-a$ 有四个不同零点, 从小到大依次为 $x_{1}, x_{2}$, $x_{3}, x_{4}$ ，则 $x_{1} x_{2}+x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n                    - \n                - 例 10\n                    - \n                    - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left|\\log _{a}\\right| 1-x| |(a>0, a \\neq 1)$, 若 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$,\n                    - 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $\\frac{1}{x_{1}}+\\frac{1}{x_{2}}+\\frac{1}{x_{3}}+\\frac{1}{x_{4}}=$ $\\qquad$ .\n                    - \n                - 练 10-1\n                    - \n                    - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\\left|\\log _{4} x\\right|, 0<x<4 \\\\ \\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi x}{2}\\right), 4 \\leqslant x \\leqslant 8\\end{array}\\right.$, 若存在实数 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}, x_{4}$ 满足 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$, 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $x_{1} x_{2} x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n                    - \n                - 练 10-2\n                    - \n                    - 设函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}-x^{2}-2 x, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ |\\ln x|, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 现有如下命题, (1)若方程 $f(x)=a$ 有四个不同的实根 $x_{1} 、 x_{2}$ 、 $x_{3} 、 x_{4}$, 则 $x_{1} \\cdot x_{2} \\cdot x_{3} \\cdot x_{4}$ 的取值范围是 $(0,1)$; (2)方程 $f^{2}(x)-\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right) f(x)+1=0$ 的不同实根的个数只能是 $1,2,3,8$. 下列判断正确的是（）\n                    - A. (1)和(2)均为真命题\n                    - B. (1)和(2)均为假命题\n                    - C. (1)为真命题，(2)为假命题\n                    - D. (1)为假命题，(2)为真命题\n                - \n        - [03函数的图像与零点问题","target":"xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题.md","line":761},{"title":"绝对值函数","target":"../绝对值函数.md","line":790},{"title":"分段函数","target":"../分段函数.md","line":794},{"title":"绝对值讨论","target":"../绝对值讨论.md","line":794},{"title":"轮换","target":"../轮换.md","line":814},{"title":"绝对值函数的理解","target":"xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题/03函数的图像与零点问题补充/绝对值函数的理解.md","line":820},{"title":"绝对值讨论 产出分段函数\n\n","target":"xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题/03函数的图像与零点问题补充/绝对值讨论 产出分段函数.md","line":822},{"title":"穿针引线","target":"../穿针引线.md","line":837},{"title":"多选题\n设 a \\ne 0，若 x = a 为函数 f(x) = a(x - a)^2(x - b) 的极大值点，则 ( )","target":"../穿针引线/穿针引线  与极值点 的考点/多选题\n设 a _ne 0，若 x = a 为函数 f(x","line":840},{"title":"概率","target":"../概率.md","line":848},{"title":"概率","target":"../概率.md","line":1125},{"title":"~扩展","target":"../~/~扩展.md","line":1430},{"title":"分式函数","target":"../分式函数.md","line":1430},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1431},{"title":"~扩展","target":"../~/~扩展.md","line":1460},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1461},{"title":"1,+\\infty)$\n                    - a\n                    - [~扩展","target":"../~/~扩展.md","line":1468},{"title":"Last Updated","target":"../CardPriority/Last Updated.md","line":1471},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\n                    - d\n                    - [~扩展","target":"../~/~扩展.md","line":1476},{"title":"Last Updated","